{"filecontent":null,"copy":"<div data-component-theme="portalThemeColor3" class="row sectionBlockLayout text-start" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0px; min-height: auto; padding: 8px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <div class="col-lg-12 columnBlockLayout" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 300px;">
      <h2 style="text-align: left;">Welcome to the Event Registration!</h2>
      <div class="row sectionBlockLayout" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 8px; margin: 0px; min-height: 15px;"></div>
      <p>​​​​🎉 Join Amazing Events Effortlessly! Explore workshops, webinars, conferences, and community gatherings—all in one place.<br />&nbsp;Sign up and stay connected to the experiences that matter.<br /><br />&nbsp;Why You’ll Love Registering with us: <br /><br />&nbsp;✅ Quick &amp; Easy: Register in just a few clicks <br />&nbsp;📅 Stay Informed: Instant Gmail notifications for confirmation and updates<br />&nbsp;🌟 All Event Details: Dates, locations, agendas, and speakers at a glance <br />&nbsp;🔒 Safe &amp; Secure: Your information is protected<br />&nbsp;🤝 Connect &amp; Network: Meaningful opportunities to learn and grow <br /><br /><br /></p>
      <a href="/Events" class="btn button1" style="background-color: rgba(254, 160, 2, 1);">Available Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div data-component-theme="portalThemeColor1" class="row sectionBlockLayout text-start" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0px; min-height: auto; padding: 8px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <div class="col-lg-6 columnBlockLayout" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 250px;">
      <h3 style="text-align: left;">💡 How It Works</h3>
      <div class="row sectionBlockLayout" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 8px; margin: 0px; min-height: 15px;"></div>
      <p style="text-align: left; width: 304px; max-width: 100%;">​📅 Upcoming Events – Browse a list of workshops, webinars, conferences, and community sessions. <br />📝 Easy Registration – Sign in and complete a quick, hassle-free registration form. <br />📧 Instant Email Notifications – Receive Gmail confirmation emails, updates, and reminders.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 columnBlockLayout" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 250px;">
      <h3 style="text-align: left;">✨ Event Features</h3>
      <div class="row sectionBlockLayout" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 8px; margin: 0px; min-height: 15px;"></div>
      <p style="width: 313px; max-width: 100%;">​🔍 Detailed Event Information – View event dates, locations, agendas, and speaker details. <br />🔒 Secure Access – Your personal information is protected with a secure sign-in process. <br />&nbsp;🤝 Learn &amp; Connect – Join events to gain knowledge and network with other participants.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div data-component-theme="portalThemeColor1" class="row sectionBlockLayout text-start" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0px; min-height: auto; padding: 8px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 0px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <div class="col-lg-12 columnBlockLayout" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 250px;"><p style="text-align: center;">🚀 Don’t Miss Out! Discover exciting events, connect with experts, and gain valuable knowledge.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>
